>>LISA: Great.

00:21:02.845 --> 00:21:03.100 align:middle line:84%
>>TWIST: And a
children's version.

00:21:03.100 --> 00:21:04.660 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So it's a whole
curriculum that can be--

00:21:04.660 --> 00:21:05.490 align:middle line:90%
>>TWIST: A whole curriculum.

