00:38:28.592 --> 00:38:29.175 align:middle line:90%
>>TWIST: And--

00:38:29.175 --> 00:38:29.470 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: --solve.

00:38:29.470 --> 00:38:30.000 align:middle line:90%
>>TWIST: --unconciously.

00:38:30.000 --> 00:38:30.290 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:38:30.290 --> 00:38:30.860 align:middle line:90%
>>TWIST: Unconciously.

00:38:30.860 --> 00:38:31.760 align:middle line:90%
But when you wake up--

00:38:31.760 --> 00:38:32.510 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Can solve.

00:38:32.510 --> 00:38:34.064 align:middle line:84%
>>TWIST: --you
just wouldn't think

00:38:34.064 --> 00:38:35.230 align:middle line:90%
