00:38:35.230 --> 00:38:35.720 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:38:35.720 --> 00:38:37.480 align:middle line:84%
>>TWIST: So that's why
a program like this

00:38:37.480 --> 00:38:40.530 align:middle line:84%
