00:41:15.090 --> 00:41:16.840 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it's really
an incredible story

00:41:16.840 --> 00:41:19.644 align:middle line:84%
and that's why I so
appreciate you being here

00:41:19.644 --> 00:41:21.560 align:middle line:84%
and that's why I'm so
