01:11:14.410 --> 01:11:17.280 align:middle line:84%
the women that I was
referring to earlier,

01:11:17.280 --> 01:11:20.940 align:middle line:90%
they have tremendous assets.

01:11:20.940 --> 01:11:22.410 align:middle line:84%
Now, the assets
aren't financial.

01:11:22.410 --> 01:11:25.000 align:middle line:84%
We think of assets
