01:12:32.380 --> 01:12:35.270 align:middle line:84%
that we needed to
partner in a sisterhood

01:12:35.270 --> 01:12:37.180 align:middle line:90%
as co-equal partners.

01:12:37.180 --> 01:12:41.380 align:middle line:84%
The women in New York having
assets of money, influence,

01:12:41.380 --> 01:12:43.980 align:middle line:84%
leisure time, and the
capacity to travel.

01:12:43.980 --> 01:12:46.500 align:middle line:84%
The women in Ethiopia
having the local language,

01:12:46.500 --> 01:12:48.950 align:middle line:84%
a fierce commitment
to eradicating hunger

01:12:48.950 --> 01:12:51.680 align:middle line:84%
in their country, a fierce
commitment to getting educated,

01:12:51.680 --> 01:12:54.860 align:middle line:84%
a fierce commitment to keeping
their tribal ways intact.

01:12:54.860 --> 01:12:57.930 align:middle line:84%
And if we put those assets
and these assets together,

01:12:57.930 --> 01:13:00.850 align:middle line:84%
